dct_description_sm: At top: Library atlas of the world. [Africa detail maps.]. 98. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Maps include: Réunion and the Mascarene Islands -- Johannesburg, Pretoria, and the Rand -- Cape Town and vicinity -- Site of Lourenc̦o Marques -- Madagascar -- Site of Durban (Port Natal) -- Ceuta -- Zanzibar Island -- Ascension Island -- Island of St. Helena -- Basin of the lower Congo -- Mauritius Island. From: The library atlas of the world. Chicago, New York : Rand McNally & Co., c1912.
